      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, a specimen that reflects a standard of care rarely encountered on the secondary market. The exterior retains its factory-level brilliance, complemented by an interior that remains in pristine, showroom-quality condition. Meticulously maintained and mechanically beyond reproach, this automobile offers an unparalleled driving experience for the most discerning collector. This is an exceptional opportunity to secure a vehicle of distinguished pedigree and flawless presentation.",
      "price": 46500.0,
